select.id: select要介護認定調査督促状ByKey

mapper.select:
SELECT "DbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho".*, "DbT5910NinteichosaItakusakiJoho"."dbT5910NinteichosaItakusakiJoho_jigyoshaMeisho", "DbT5910NinteichosaItakusakiJoho"."dbT5910NinteichosaItakusakiJoho_yubinNo", "DbT5910NinteichosaItakusakiJoho"."dbT5910NinteichosaItakusakiJoho_jusho", "DbT5913ChosainJoho"."dbT5913ChosainJoho_chosainShimei"
FROM () AS "DbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho"
INNER JOIN ( SELECT DbT5201.*, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY DbT5201."dbT5201NinteichosaIraiJoho_shinseishoKanriNo", DbT5201."dbT5201NinteichosaIraiJoho_ninteichosaIraiRirekiNo" ORDER BY DbT5201."dbT5201NinteichosaIraiJoho_ninteichosaIraiRirekiNo" DESC) AS "rowNum" FROM () AS DbT5201 ) AS "DbT5201NinteichosaIraiJoho" ON "DbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho"."dbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho_shinseishoKanriNo" = "DbT5201NinteichosaIraiJoho"."dbT5201NinteichosaIraiJoho_shinseishoKanriNo" AND "DbT5201NinteichosaIraiJoho"."rowNum" = 1
AND "DbT5201NinteichosaIraiJoho"."dbT5201NinteichosaIraiJoho_ninteichosaKigenYMD" < #{temp_認定調査督促期限}
AND ("DbT5201NinteichosaIraiJoho"."dbT5201NinteichosaIraiJoho_ninteichosaTokusokuYMD" IS NULL OR "DbT5201NinteichosaIraiJoho"."dbT5201NinteichosaIraiJoho_ninteichosaTokusokuYMD" = '')
INNER JOIN () AS "DbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho" ON "DbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho"."dbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho_shinseishoKanriNo" = "DbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho"."dbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho_shinseishoKanriNo" AND ("DbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho"."dbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho_ninteiShinseiJohoTorokuKanryoYMD" IS NOT NULL AND "DbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho"."dbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho_ninteiShinseiJohoTorokuKanryoYMD" != '') AND ("DbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho"."dbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho_ninteichosaIraiKanryoYMD" IS NOT NULL AND "DbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho"."dbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho_ninteichosaIraiKanryoYMD" != '') AND ("DbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho"."dbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho_ninteichosaKanryoYMD" IS NULL OR "DbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho"."dbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho_ninteichosaKanryoYMD" = '') AND ("DbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho"."dbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho_ninteichosaKanryoYMD" IS NULL OR "DbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho"."dbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho_ninteichosaKanryoYMD" = '') AND ("DbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho"."dbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho_ninteiShinsakaiWariateKanryoYMD" IS NULL OR "DbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho"."dbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho_ninteiShinsakaiWariateKanryoYMD" = '') AND ("DbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho"."dbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho_ninteiShinsakaiKanryoYMD" IS NULL OR "DbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho"."dbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho_ninteiShinsakaiKanryoYMD" = '') AND ("DbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho"."dbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho_centerSoshinYMD" IS NULL OR "DbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho"."dbT5105NinteiKanryoJoho_centerSoshinYMD" = '')
LEFT JOIN () AS "DbT7051KoseiShichosonMaster" ON "DbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho"."dbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho_shoKisaiHokenshaNo" = "DbT7051KoseiShichosonMaster"."dbT7051KoseiShichosonMaster_shoKisaiHokenshaNo"
LEFT JOIN () AS "DbT5910NinteichosaItakusakiJoho" ON "DbT7051KoseiShichosonMaster"."dbT7051KoseiShichosonMaster_shichosonCode" = "DbT5910NinteichosaItakusakiJoho"."dbT5910NinteichosaItakusakiJoho_shichosonCode" AND "DbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho"."dbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho_ninteiChosaItakusakiCode" = "DbT5910NinteichosaItakusakiJoho"."dbT5910NinteichosaItakusakiJoho_ninteichosaItakusakiCode"
LEFT JOIN () AS "DbT5913ChosainJoho" ON "DbT7051KoseiShichosonMaster"."dbT7051KoseiShichosonMaster_shichosonCode" = "DbT5913ChosainJoho"."dbT5913ChosainJoho_shichosonCode" AND "DbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho"."dbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho_ninteiChosaItakusakiCode" = "DbT5913ChosainJoho"."dbT5913ChosainJoho_ninteiChosaItakusakiCode" AND "DbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho"."dbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho_ninteiChosainCode" = "DbT5913ChosainJoho"."dbT5913ChosainJoho_ninteiChosainCode"
1 = 1
AND "DbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho"."dbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho_shoKisaiHokenshaNo" = #{temp_保険者コード}
AND "DbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho"."dbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho_ninteiChosaItakusakiCode" = #{temp_認定調査委託先コード}
AND "DbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho"."dbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho_ninteiChosainCode" = #{temp_認定調査員コード}
AND "DbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho"."dbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho_shoriJotaiKubun" != '1' AND "DbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho"."dbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho_shoriJotaiKubun" != '2' ORDER BY "DbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho"."dbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho_shoKisaiHokenshaNo", "DbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho"."dbT5101NinteiShinseiJoho_hihokenshaKana"

select.id: select認定調査督促対象者一覧表ByKey

mapper.select: SELECT DbT7051."shichosonCode" AS shichosonCode FROM rgdb."DbT7051KoseiShichosonMaster" AS DbT7051 WHERE DbT7051."shoKisaiHokenshaNo" = #{保険者コード} LIMIT 1

SELECT DbT5910."jigyoshaMeisho" AS 宛名機関名, DbT5910."yubinNo" AS 宛名郵便番号, DbT5910."jusho" AS 宛名住所, DbT5913."chosainShimei" AS 宛名氏名 FROM rgdb."DbT5913ChosainJoho" AS DbT5913 LEFT JOIN rgdb."DbT5910NinteichosaItakusakiJoho" AS DbT5910 ON DbT5913."shichosonCode" = DbT5910."shichosonCode" AND DbT5913."ninteiChosaItakusakiCode" = DbT5910."ninteichosaItakusakiCode" WHERE DbT5913."ninteiChosaItakusakiCode" = #{temp_認定調査委託先コード} AND DbT5913."ninteiChosainCode" = #{temp_認定調査員コード} AND DbT5913."shichosonCode" = #{temp_市町村コード}
